curam.util.client.domain

Class AbstractClientDomainPlugIn

  • java.lang.Object
    • curam.util.common.plugin.AbstractPlugIn
      • curam.util.common.domain.AbstractDomainPlugIn
        • curam.util.client.domain.AbstractClientDomainPlugIn
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DomainPlugIn, PlugIn
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbstractComparator, AbstractConverter, AbstractDefault

    public abstract class AbstractClientDomainPlugIn
extends AbstractDomainPlugIn

    A base class for client domain plug-ins. This adds some utility methods to the AbstractDomainPlugIn that make it easier for client domain plug-in implementations to access other types of plug-ins configured for the same domain.

    Direct access to this class, or extensions to this class are not supported from custom code. This documentation is included only to facilitate the navigation of the public Javadoc.
